{"title":"Wolf Tooth Adds Larger Direct-Mount Shimano Chainrings + All Limited Edition Ti Cages on Sale","link":"https://bikerumor.com/wolf-tooth-larger-direct-mount-shimano-mtb-chainrings-limited-edition-ti-cages-sale/","date":1692029509000,"content":"<p><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-New-DM-Shimano-Chainrings-riding.jpeg\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth New DM Shimano Chainrings riding\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-New-DM-Shimano-Chainrings-riding.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-New-DM-Shimano-Chainrings-riding-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-New-DM-Shimano-Chainrings-riding-800x534.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-New-DM-Shimano-Chainrings-riding-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-New-DM-Shimano-Chainrings-riding-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-New-DM-Shimano-Chainrings-riding-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>At Minnesota’s bike bling HQ, Wolf Tooth Components has responded to their customer’s calls for bigger Shimano chainrings. As a result, they have  released new, larger Drop-Stop ST Chainrings for Shimano mountain cranks. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-New-DM-Shimano-Chainrings-chain-ring.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-New-DM-Shimano-Chainrings-chain-ring-800x534.jpeg\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth New DM Shimano Chainrings chain ring\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-New-DM-Shimano-Chainrings-chain-ring-800x534.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-New-DM-Shimano-Chainrings-chain-ring-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-New-DM-Shimano-Chainrings-chain-ring-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-New-DM-Shimano-Chainrings-chain-ring-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-New-DM-Shimano-Chainrings-chain-ring-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-New-DM-Shimano-Chainrings-chain-ring.jpeg 1280w\" /></a><figcaption>Photo c. Wolf Tooth Components</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>These new Shimano chainrings are still designed and machined in Minnesota with the impeccable attention to detail that we’ve come to expect from Wolf Tooth Components. You can expect them in the following sizes: 30, 32, 34, 36, and 38T round as well as 32, 34, 36T oval sizes. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-Shimano-ST-Drop-stop-chainring-round.jpeg\"><img width=\"590\" height=\"590\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-Shimano-ST-Drop-stop-chainring-round.jpeg\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth Shimano ST Drop stop chainring round\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-Shimano-ST-Drop-stop-chainring-round.jpeg 590w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-Shimano-ST-Drop-stop-chainring-round-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-Shimano-ST-Drop-stop-chainring-round-120x120.jpeg 120w\" /></a><figcaption>Shimano ST Drop-Stop round chainring</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-Shimano-ST-Drop-stop-chainring-oval.jpeg\"><img width=\"590\" height=\"590\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-Shimano-ST-Drop-stop-chainring-oval.jpeg\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth Shimano ST Drop stop chainring oval\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-Shimano-ST-Drop-stop-chainring-oval.jpeg 590w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-Shimano-ST-Drop-stop-chainring-oval-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-Shimano-ST-Drop-stop-chainring-oval-120x120.jpeg 120w\" /></a><figcaption>Shimano ST Drop-Stop oval chainring</figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Wolf Tooth Drop-Stop ST tooth profile is optimized for Shimano HG+ chains and retails for $79.95 (round), and $86.95 (oval).</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Bonus News!</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3>Sale on ALL Limited Edition Morse Ti Bottle Cages</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-Limited-Edition-Morse-Ti-Cage-in-pink.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-Limited-Edition-Morse-Ti-Cage-in-pink-800x534.jpeg\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth Limited Edition Morse Ti Cage in pink\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-Limited-Edition-Morse-Ti-Cage-in-pink-800x534.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-Limited-Edition-Morse-Ti-Cage-in-pink-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-Limited-Edition-Morse-Ti-Cage-in-pink-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-Limited-Edition-Morse-Ti-Cage-in-pink-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-Limited-Edition-Morse-Ti-Cage-in-pink-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-Limited-Edition-Morse-Ti-Cage-in-pink.jpeg 1024w\" /></a><figcaption>Limited Edition Morse Ti Cage in pink.</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>That’s right, right now you can take 25% off of <em>all</em> <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=18985&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wolftoothcomponents.com%2Fcollections%2Fbottle-cages\" target=\"_blank\">Limited Edition Morse Ti Cages</a> through Labor Day! </p>\n\n\n\n<p>For the Limited Edition Morse Ti Cages, Wolf Tooth adds a <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wolf-tooth-limited-edition-green-morse-cage/\" target=\"_blank\">Cerakote finish</a> to their standard titanium bottle cages. If you didn’t already know, Cerakote is a durable industrial strength coating that is often used for tools, engines, and now bikes. It has a uniquely durable matte finish that can hold up to a lot of abuse. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>All Morse cages are hand-bent in Wolf Tooth’s Minnesota, USA machine shop. Colors available are Pink, Teal, Khaki, Copper, Orange, Green, and Red. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Sale on select Muli-Tools </h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-multi-tools.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-multi-tools-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth multi-tools\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-multi-tools-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-multi-tools-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-multi-tools-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-multi-tools-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-multi-tools-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth-multi-tools.jpeg 1200w\" /></a><figcaption>6-Bit Hex Wrench Multi-Tool.</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Yup, today is the last day to take 25% off of select Wolf Tooth Multi Tools, like this<a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/review-wolf-tooth-components-great-edc-multi-tool/\" target=\"_blank\"> lil’ game changer</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>These useful and handy tools are designed and machined in-house in Wolf Tooth’s facility in Minnesota, USA. These gems are small, modular, and super functional solutions for eliminating trailside situations that may hinder your ride. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The tools that are included in the sale are the 6-Bit Hex Wrench, 8-Bit System, and EnCase System Multi-Tools. Some details on the tools are below.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>6-Bit Hex Wrench</strong> – <em>slim, strong multi-tool with 11 functions for common bike repairs and everyday needs</em>. (Retail: $ $39.95 <strong>Sale price: $29.96</strong>)</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>8-Bit System</strong> – <em>covers 25+ functions to eliminate most trailside problems with four unique multi-tools.</em> (Retail: $ $69.95 <strong>Sale price: $52.46</strong>)</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>EnCase System</strong> – <em>a pair of innovative multi-tools that are stored in handlebar ends during rides so you can quickly access their 14 functions while on the trail.</em> (Retail: $ $119.95 <strong>Sale price: $89.96</strong>)</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Check all of the info and get your own at the link below. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=18985&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wolftoothcomponents.com%2F\" target=\"_blank\">WolfToothComponents.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wolf-tooth-larger-direct-mount-shimano-mtb-chainrings-limited-edition-ti-cages-sale/\">Wolf Tooth Adds Larger Direct-Mount Shimano Chainrings + All Limited Edition Ti Cages on Sale</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"5c44074bdec0ed9b0fa169c5ab8bf2b3c08730b6844257491474ca455b251a61","category":"Cycling"}